246
00:21:56,532 --> 00:21:58,832
もりもりmany-many返すから！
I'll return it with many-many more!

247
00:21:58,832 --> 00:22:02,132
いつだって しゅきしゅきしゅきしゅきスプリームなお願い聞いて！
Always, listen to my shuki-shuki Supreme request!

248
00:22:02,132 --> 00:22:05,532
わたし会いたーい
I want to see you.

249
00:22:07,132 --> 00:22:09,632
Day by day ちょーmany-manyぎゅーぎゅぎゅっとエールをリリース
Day by day, super many-many gyu-gyu-gyutto cheer, delivered to you.

250
00:22:09,632 --> 00:22:12,832
絶対ゼッタイ倍で返すから！
I'll return it, absolutely, absolutely double!

251
00:22:14,532 --> 00:22:16,832
手渡しじゃ何年かかっても
Even if it takes years to hand it over,

252
00:22:17,432 --> 00:22:18,832
会いたいじゃない！ 届けたいじゃない！
I want to see you! I want to reach you!

253
00:22:18,832 --> 00:22:21,532
Gimme!! いつも愛をアリ・ガ・トゥー
Gimme!! Always, love, th-a-n-k y-o-u!

254
00:22:22,032 --> 00:22:23,032
もっみゅん♡
Momyun! ♡

255
00:22:23,032 --> 00:22:25,132
きゅっきゅん らたっちゅら めにめに Oh yeah
Kyu-kyun ratacchura meni-meni Oh yeah

256
00:22:25,132 --> 00:22:27,532
きゅんきゅんきゅんとくんとー？
Kyun-kyun-kyun tokun-to?

257
00:22:27,532 --> 00:22:28,532
きゅんきゅんきゅんとくんとー？
Kyun-kyun-kyun tokun-to?

258
00:22:28,532 --> 00:22:30,832
きゅんきゅんきゅんきゅんきゅんきゅん！
Kyun-kyun-kyun-kyun-kyun-kyun!

259
00:22:30,832 --> 00:22:33,032
ずーっとよろしくね！
Always be with me, okay!

260
00:22:39,532 --> 00:22:45,332
ゆらゆらり はらはらり
いろとりどり みだれ咲き
Swaying gently, fluttering down,
In a riot of colors, blooming wildly.

261
00:22:45,332 --> 00:22:49,832
花の街 思い出す
この空から
From this sky,
I remember the city of flowers.

262
00:22:51,532 --> 00:22:53,032
[Title: 百花繚乱]
[Title: Hyakka Ryoran (Profusion of Flowers)]

263
00:22:58,532 --> 00:23:04,532
ひょんな出来事から やってきたこの場所は
Through an unexpected turn of events, I arrived at this place,

264
00:23:04,532 --> 00:23:10,532
遥か遠くにあった 煌びやかな舞台
A glittering stage that once seemed so far away.

265
00:23:10,532 --> 00:23:16,832
ハッとするほど鮮やかな世界が あるんだと知った
I learned that a world so breathtakingly vivid truly exists,

266
00:23:16,832 --> 00:23:22,532
あなたの無理難題に 答えていく どんな旅に
Responding to your impossible demands, on whatever journey it may be.

267
00:23:23,532 --> 00:23:29,532
あっと言わせるような奇想天外な 答え合わせで
With an astonishing, out-of-the-box checking of answers,

268
00:23:29,532 --> 00:23:36,532
辿り着いたその先に 新しい景色が待っているんだ
A new landscape is waiting at the end of the road we've reached.

269
00:23:42,532 --> 00:23:49,032
摩訶不思議なミステリー 次から次に起こるたび
Every time a profound mystery occurs one after another,

270
00:23:49,032 --> 00:23:55,532
巧妙なからくりも 暴いてみせましょう
I'll expose even the most ingenious mechanisms.

271
00:23:55,532 --> 00:24:02,032
どんな難題でも 種や仕掛けはあるんだ
No matter how difficult the problem, there's always a trick or a gimmick.

272
00:24:02,032 --> 00:24:08,532
副作用は気にしない 必ず闇導き出すから
I don't care about side effects; I'll definitely lead us out of the darkness.

273
00:24:26,532 --> 00:24:32,532
あぁ この場所で触れた 人の悲しみや喜びがある
Ah, in this place, there are the sorrows and joys of the people I've touched.

274
00:24:32,532 --> 00:24:40,032
そのひとつひとつが 心を震わせる
