275
00:24:40,532 --> 00:24:46,032
はっとしちゃうほど鮮やかな世界が ここにあるんだ
A world so vivid it takes your breath away is right here.

276
00:24:46,032 --> 00:24:52,532
あなたの無理難題に 答えていく毎日に
In these days of responding to your impossible demands,

277
00:24:52,532 --> 00:25:00,032
あっと言わせるような奇想天外な 答え合わせで
With an astonishing, out-of-the-box checking of answers...

278
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,840
...辿り着いたその先に
...reached that destination,

279
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:04,540
新しい私が待っているんだ
a new version of me is waiting.

280
00:25:07,040 --> 00:25:10,540
あの頃は 想像もしてない
Back then, I couldn't even imagine

281
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:14,540
未来が咲き始めてる
that the future would start to bloom.

282
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:18,540
こんな日々も悪くはないかな
Maybe these days aren't so bad.

283
00:25:25,540 --> 00:25:28,040
ゆらり ひらり
Swaying, fluttering,

284
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:31,540
離れては 寄り添って
drifting apart then drawing close.

285
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:34,540
そよぐ風に身を任せ
Entrusting my body to the gentle breeze,

286
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:38,040
夕闇に舞う
I dance in the twilight.

287
00:25:43,040 --> 00:25:46,040
KONNANじゃないっ!
[Title: Not Like This!]

288
00:25:58,040 --> 00:26:00,840
アノユメも アコガレも
Those dreams, that admiration,

289
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:04,540
落書きのままボヤけて
blurring while still just graffiti,

290
00:26:05,540 --> 00:26:07,540
消えろ寸前
