"Is this okay?" "Is this really okay?"

292
00:26:13,540 --> 00:26:17,540
ふてくされてる鏡に
To my sulking mirror,

293
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:21,040
何度も問いかけた
I questioned again and again.

294
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:24,540
泣きたい日も
Even on days I want to cry,

295
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:28,040
くじけそうな日も
even on days I feel like giving up,

296
00:26:28,540 --> 00:26:31,540
乗り越えよう
let's overcome it.

297
00:26:33,540 --> 00:26:37,540
希望を浴びなきゃ
Unless I bathe in hope,

298
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:42,540
夢というツボミは
the flower bud of my dream

299
00:26:42,540 --> 00:26:45,540
開かないから
