300
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:49,840
Are you ready GO! 走り出そう!
Are you ready GO! Let's start running!

301
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:52,540
取り急ぎ さぁスタート!
In a hurry, start now!

302
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:56,540
うつむかない! ふりむかない!
Don't look down! Don't look back!

303
00:26:56,540 --> 00:26:59,040
明日は絶対もっとShiny!
Tomorrow will definitely be even more Shiny!

304
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:02,540
ジブン次第! 掴め未来!
It's up to me! Seize the future!

305
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:05,540
今すぐスタートボタン
Let's press the start button

306
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:08,040
押してみよう
right now.

307
00:27:08,540 --> 00:27:12,040
私は こんなんじゃないはず!
I am, this can't be all there is!

308
00:27:25,040 --> 00:27:26,540
3, 2, 1, GO!

309
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:41,540
あきらめも 言い訳も
Bundle up the resignation and excuses

310
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:44,040
取りまとめリスタート!
and let's restart!

311
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:47,040
『たられば』に すがるには
Are you still too young

312
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:50,540
まだまだ若すぎじゃない?
to cling to "if onlys"?

313
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:53,840
七転び八起きでGO!
Fall seven times, rise eight, GO!

314
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:56,540
何度もリセットボタン
No matter how many times I press the reset button,

315
00:27:57,040 --> 00:28:00,540
どんな夢も きっと
surely, any dream

316
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:04,540
困難じゃないはず
won't be difficult.

317
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:08,540
信じてみよう
Believe in it.

318
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:12,040
私は こんなんじゃないはず!
I am, this can't be all there is!

319
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:28,040
Are you ready GO!

320
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:31,040
もう一回セーノ!
One more time, ready!

321
00:28:32,540 --> 00:28:35,540
ハイ! ハイ! ゼンリョク!
Hai! Hai! Full power!

322
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:39,540
私は こんなんじゃない!
I am, this can't be all there is!

323
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:53,040
Great Days
[Title: Great Days]

324
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:08,040
Shining justice 芽生えてく
Shining justice, starts to bloom

325
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:13,540
Brand new bed town 交差する息吹
Brand new bed town, a fresh breath arrives

326
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:19,540
岬から潮風 トンネル抜け鉄塔へ
A sea breeze from that tunnel, heading for the tower

327
00:29:20,540 --> 00:29:25,540
引かれ合い小道に迷い込む
Drawn to one another, losing our way down lanes

328
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:31,040
ココロに溶け込む影
