330
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:41,040
それは守り抜く光
A light to protect our only one

331
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:47,040
Let the voice of love take you higher!

332
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:52,540
集まるチカラで時さえ越えて
